{"tid":1496493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人善忘？為何放過新城市廣場？放過支持送中的店？","createTime":"2019-08-22T14:23:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T13:26:31.000Z","uid":269717,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"56f687f8e3b2c9d0df14bc275c0d240fe5767a60","tid":1496493,"uid":269717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:23:29.000Z","msg":"如題。要持續把新城市搞到痛苦不堪，店鋪關門。把支持送中的餐飲店搞到無法營業。要讓香港所有人知道支持黑警和港共政府是有巨大代價的。不用暴力就能達到效果。機場一定要每週去至少一次，讓政府崩潰。<br />\n<br />\n你不讓別人感到痛，別人就根本不理你。818過去幾天，得到了noted with thanks 還有其他的嗎？和理非去新城市，去機場，去店鋪照樣能有巨大效果，還不用送頭。<br />\n<br />\n比如100人堵一芳，100人堵吉野家，讓所有人知道，支持魔鬼是有代價的。我們不能讓手足白死，白白被打到骨折，打爆眼睛。要讓它們明白，是要有重大代價的"},{"pid":"878aa570f8d885555814c2baac3e193b8f6b8cf5","tid":1496493,"uid":74958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:26:26.000Z","msg":"要使革命到來，單是『下層不願』照舊生活下去、尋求改變通常是不夠的，還需要『上層不能』照舊生活和統治下去。"},{"pid":"5dc4f327a529ffca6412208298ca8fd5639ab79c","tid":1496493,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:26:58.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"c42932c0b40a15c21cf971a0b964d65e47d5c92c","tid":1496493,"uid":153722,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:27:14.000Z","msg":"依期開左咁多戰線<br />\n<br />\n點解突然會有個P牌仔跳出黎<br />\n鼓吹開反新城市同罷食食肆既?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4ca137ea2f9377ce3ca3ae0a91514dc572352b0","tid":1496493,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:29:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"264ec511c85d22f1478177f15908032f6aed3c3a","tid":1496493,"uid":50890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:36:31.000Z","msg":"新城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img