要清算警隊。警暴（濫捕、濫告、不依法規）係暴政一部分，唔全面改革警隊、監警制度，只會令目前同將來爭取雙普選更加舉步維艱<br />\n<br />\n所以，絕對唔需要否認自己係針對警隊，針對警隊就係對準政權。唔通你淨係針對林鄭、唔針對政制，就會有雙普選？<br />\n<br />\n#五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n#唔撤就罷<br />\n#罷工罷巿罷買罷課<br />\n#我係香港人<br />\n#我參與全港四罷<br />\n#各區集會<br />\n#出核彈麻包袋都唔割蓆<br />\n#直至政府跪低<br />\n#重組警隊 刑事追究 改革監警制度<br />\n#永遠不光顧荃灣北角元朗商戶<br />\n#抵制一切紅媒相關商業活動"},{"pid":"95a3fd229b84631d37895354cafaefd87f1978af","tid":1496493,"uid":153722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f714863cdd6dc12768c5bdb99d991163bac68c58","tid":1496493,"uid":269717,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c42932c0b40a15c21cf971a0b964d65e47d5c92c","tid":1496493,"uid":153722,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:27:14.000Z","msg":"依期開左咁多戰線<br />\n<br />\n點解突然會有個P牌仔跳出黎<br />\n鼓吹開反新城市同罷食食肆既?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:37:32.000Z","msg":"新城市只是一個例子<br />\n<br />\np牌不一定是五毛<br />\n<br />\n完全是為了反送中開acc而已"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:16:36.000Z","msg":"見到今日銀髮族係新城市發起既罷買行動<br />\n想講句sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"106b11a05e5e56376761e62db65d3aeb31657c00","tid":1496493,"uid":269717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95a3fd229b84631d37895354cafaefd87f1978af","tid":1496493,"uid":153722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f714863cdd6dc12768c5bdb99d991163bac68c58","tid":1496493,"uid":269717,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c42932c0b40a15c21cf971a0b964d65e47d5c92c","tid":1496493,"uid":153722,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:27:14.000Z","msg":"依期開左咁多戰線<br />\n<br />\n點解突然會有個P牌仔跳出黎<br />\n鼓吹開反新城市同罷食食肆既?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2